{"tid":967270,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"佣金1.7%爭議 中原：撤回抗議信 引起不便請發展商見諒","createTime":"2019-01-03T11:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T14:05:56.000Z","uid":220779,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"547cfe564285fec47a105778fc1562f8c61c8f1e","tid":967270,"uid":220779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T11:11:49.000Z","msg":"發展商信置日前公布觀塘凱滙的代理佣金低至1.7%，導致地產代理界不滿，當中原更罕有致函予發展商要求修訂有關佣金。<br />\n<br />\n相隔一天，中原地產發出最新回應指：「有關中原昨日去信信置對凱匯佣金意見一事，今日中原去信信置, 對於昨日中原與信置之間的書信公開引起之不便，請發展商見諒。」<br />\n<br />\n中原地產表示，今日公司已與發展商有和諧及良好的溝通，等待發展商的好消息，現先撤回昨日的抗議信。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2242628/凱滙佣金1.7%25爭議%20中原：撤回抗議信%20待發展商好消息?mtc=60007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2242628%2F%E5%87%B1%E6%BB%99%E4%BD%A3%E9%87%911.7%2525%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0%2520%E4%B8%AD%E5%8E%9F%EF%BC%9A%E6%92%A4%E5%9B%9E%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0%E4%BF%A1%2520%E5%BE%85%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%95%86%E5%A5%BD%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%3Fmtc%3D60007&d=e6R0DSEO%2BDOF4QK4gxIeYACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f0cffc7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2242628/凱滙佣金1.7%25爭議%20中原：撤回抗議信%20待發展商好消息?mtc=60007</a>"},{"pid":"e0dfaf7c149f2857c3fdb0a26ea540e01eb323b6","tid":967270,"uid":70301,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8501bf6fb0682d18557b63c5e8c32d143d655df3","tid":967270,"uid":40470,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T11:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n青山道屎都無得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n低技能抵學歷乞衣轉行又轉唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n死去做痰仔啦青山道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f3e4eccaf1a